data.name: label1.Text
data.value: The halls was filled with echoes of your voice as you shout for help. No one answered. Just like you expected. But there was no harm in trying. While wandering around the cafeteria, you notice a glass box with something written on it. It read 'For emergency use' and contained a crowbar and an axe. Not much use for an axe, but the crowbar might come in handy.
